lyrics:
[Verse 1]
In a town called sunshine, lives Miss Bea Hay-ven
A heart of gold, with a smile so free
She's the light that brightens up our days
Her love and kindness, like a gentle breeze

[Chorus]
Oh, Miss Bea Hay-ven, you bring joy to our souls
With your grace and beauty, you make us whole
Oh, Miss Bea Hay-ven, a guiding star so bright
We're blessed to have you, in our lives shining so light
